e property: `jsonString` (the string you wish to validate as JSON).", "height": 380, "width": 280, "color": 1}, "typeVersion": 1}, {"id": "f3f93504-93b2-40e9-93e6-45366a681ac0", "name": "Note: JSON Validation Logic", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "position": [-420, -320], "parameters": {"content": "## JSON Validation Logic\n\nThis node contains custom JavaScript code to parse the `jsonString` from the webhook input. It returns `valid: true` if successful, or `valid: false` with an `error` message if parsing fails.", "height": 360, "width": 350, "color": 2}, "typeVersion": 1}, {"id": "e8632087-424b-40b4-a894-301885137f49", "name": "Note: Webhook Response", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "position": [0, -320], "parameters": {"content": "## Webhook Response\n\nThis node sends the validation result (whether the `jsonString` was valid JSON or not, including an error if applicable) back to the system that triggered the webhook.", "height": 360, "width": 350, "color": 3}, "typeVersion": 1}], "connections": {"Code: Validate JSON String": {"main": [[{"node": "Respond to Webhook with Result", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Webhook: Receive JSON String": {"main": [[{"node": "Code: Validate JSON String", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}}, "settings": {"executionOrder": "v1"}, "nodeGroups": []}, "customData": {}, "_source": "/tmp/n8n_corpus/DragonJAR_n8n-workflows-esp/workflows/06122-Json-string-validator-via-webhook.json"}